{"tid":1886341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港廢藍老應該要去死","createTime":"2020-02-18T23:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T08:29:58.000Z","uid":74778,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc2cf13529ccc75af483e14e02dfad598331cfd","tid":1886341,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T23:40:35.000Z","msg":"因為<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年輕人，用<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">爭取民主自由 公民權利</span></strong>等理由去發動<span style=\"color: blue;\">罷工罷巿罷課，不合作運動</span>，藍廢老屌，話<em>手停口停、你要抗爭我唔阻你但你唔好阻我搵食，你無家庭但我一家大細等我養...</em>屌到要朝朝喺地鐵門口鬧年輕人鬧到打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好，三罷搞唔成，你繼續做港豬<br />\n<br />\n宜家，<br />\n<br />\n仆佢個臭街陷家剷大陸閪，用<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">整生化武器呢個咁損人害己嘅理由，</span></strong>播撚咗隻致命病毒出黎。又因為<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">林鄭月娥政府為咗要媚共、擦鞋，唔肯封關，要全香港做大陸逃生門！</span></strong><br />\n因為呢兩個主因，香港人心惶惶，停工停巿！餐廳、零售、酒店、司機、地盤(等大規模爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，死得嘅都死！由上以下咁手停口停！<br />\n<del></del><br />\n班仆街陷家剷死廢老們嘅反應係點呢？係咪喺政府總部門口指住林鄭月娥塊臭閪黎屌呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔係！<br />\n班仆街陷家剷係好似狗咁撚樣朝朝4 5點去各大黃店排 口 罩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班撚樣老狗快撚啲去死啦！廢物！<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"35343ca4bb61580468844246457dec970c22da35","tid":1886341,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T23:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0160681da5e4c6249d9e9ee3826787c1f756756","tid":1886341,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=